      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine currently runs roughly and will require a significant overhaul to be roadworthy again, and the transmission shifts harshly. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is being sold strictly as-is, and I recommend a trailer for transport.",
