    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a great new home. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really nice shape, perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! It\u2019s clean, runs smoothly, and has plenty of life left in it. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
